#, python-format
msgid ""
"Hallo %(user)s,\n"
"\n"
"du (oder jemand anderes) hat ein neues Passwort für dein Konto beim\n"
"Collection Management System angefordert."
msgstr ""
"Hello %(user)s,\n"
"\n"
"you (or someone else) requested a new password for your account at the\n"
"Collection Management System."

#: templates/registration/password_reset_email.txt:6
msgid "Neues Passwort festlegen:"
msgstr "Set a new password:"

#: templates/registration/password_reset_email.txt:9
msgid ""
"Falls du das nicht warst, kannst du diese E-Mail ignorieren – dein Passwort "
"bleibt unverändert."
msgstr ""
"If this wasn't you, you can ignore this e-mail – your password stays "
"unchanged."

#: templates/registration/password_reset_form.html:3
#: templates/registration/password_reset_form.html:9
msgid "Passwort zurücksetzen"
msgstr "Reset password"

#: templates/registration/password_reset_form.html:11
msgid ""
"Gib die E-Mail-Adresse deines Kontos an. Du erhältst einen Link, mit dem du "
"ein neues Passwort festlegen kannst."
msgstr ""
"Enter the e-mail address of your account. You will receive a link that lets "
"you set a new password."

#: templates/registration/password_reset_form.html:22
msgid "Link anfordern"
msgstr "Request link"

#: templates/registration/password_reset_subject.txt:1
msgid "Passwort zurücksetzen – Collection Management System"
msgstr "Reset your password – Collection Management System"

#: templates/registration/register.html:9
msgid "Konto erstellen"
msgstr "Create account"

#: templates/registration/register.html:11
msgid ""
"Neue Konten werden erst nach Freigabe durch einen Administrator aktiv. Nach "
"der Registrierung kannst du dich anmelden, sobald deine Freigabe erfolgt ist."
msgstr ""
"New accounts become active only after approval by an administrator. After "
"registering you can sign in once your approval has been granted."

#: templates/registration/register.html:30
msgid "Schon ein Konto?"
msgstr "Already have an account?"
